# Centralized Security (CSS)

- Auth for new/migrated apps uses **CSS** at `E:\MyWorkspace\centralized-security-system` (**port 9000**).
- Do not build a separate login/JWT issuer per app without explicit user confirmation.
- Register `clientId` in `workflow/css/CLIENT-REGISTRY.md` before wiring.
- On promote: also record **CSS version + git tag** from `workflow/deps/` (not only clientId).
- Spring apps: prefer `css-spring-boot-starter`; validate via JWKS (RS256).
- Public auth via nginx `/auth/` on delena.buzz when exposed; not raw public IP in configs.
- Details: `workflow/css/README.md`, `workflow/deps/README.md`, and CSS repo `docs/application-integration.md`
